      <title>Stanley M. Gartler, Pioneer in Cancer Research, Dies at 102</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/04/science/stanley-m-gartler-dead.html</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/04/science/stanley-m-gartler-dead.html</guid>
